Guinea Pig Adventure 1
http://www.deater.net/vmwprod/gp1/

by Vince Weaver
vince@deater.net

Background
~~~~~~~~~~
A rpg adventure game written as an exercise in learning OpenGL.

Instructions
~~~~~~~~~~~~
Use arrows/joystick to move.
'A' and 'Z' change altitude
'I' 'J' 'K' 'M' change camera angle
'L' toggles lighting effects

Command Line Options
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
--halfsize   runs in 320x200 mode
